paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-62c98a12-bffa-4de7-97f2-334da16f5dbc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4485fe2-d861-49a3-af33-20588f81947a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">A4 사이즈 안에 들어가는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-72493f3c-00bb-4725-82e2-ec3688a266df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a1113e6a-69c8-44ea-a050-e2d780cc5b33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자의 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bcc2f344-07f0-490f-8bfd-b886b9ddf4e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1990e158-3dbf-410e-9358-51aa6080034f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2887df99-200f-498f-9b2e-b7b6986208e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6d0f456-d1bb-4b4c-a4b7-1acd53d56c25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">200개 기준으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-90b7b19b-6089-49e8-84ab-33f13197c837\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea9bf8c9-e42d-4098-b626-334d9e6de1cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털과 오프셋이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1c60280e-06dd-4f50-8c60-d18e81e29293\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42d67186-97ed-4279-8978-cedc72c2f51c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">비슷한 단가로 생산될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5945099e-813a-4017-8523-e52891b4c9cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4de78194-977a-4fe8-9e4f-fcb8ef62800b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-26cb6eb0-e13e-41b5-a5e9-66b32ffb0f34\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2fe57b8-cf55-4941-87cd-f1687a2dc6b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">300개가 넘어가면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-77887f12-f271-4634-aac9-1d2a0b1f54a7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-acaa9ce0-96a4-4ea2-b7c3-5f7271029f1d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오프셋이 저렴해지기 시작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1ebf9e9c-0c91-44f5-af10-07e69f636f3d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58f09daa-d1fa-4eee-a6b1-dd4e0830ce77\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e11f245a-f264-47f8-aea4-071f24deaf8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b368f0e0-6807-4980-99f1-83adc1b7a61f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납기는 오프셋이 당연히 느립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9fb8e55b-5c9f-4474-9d6b-d97ae6c591b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-45dbf673-77ad-43e0-bf02-28ba2914efd5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">통상의 경우 500개 기준으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ef9f5a25-5ac6-4063-a661-09f72539e47d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99e3be26-b654-4af4-bdce-c85899e4658f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">납기는 5~7일 사이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-11bfb28b-e1a3-486e-aa11-71a3a8932580\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd32d864-312c-42bd-a419-12c74250ead6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-935415b0-d396-4e9d-9ea9-d204683ecaba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3687ca2-1c3b-4e63-899b-488214d68ff8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7e75b47d-1092-457c-a106-e4e220128b42\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2a9cdb0-b53c-4b39-a2a5-eb82224d0752\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9d96bb5c-01d2-4740-a618-9f776251a8d2\" style=\"\">디지털 / 오프셋 비교</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2c7ffef5-df5c-4970-b750-f0b2cef1d853\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-431edbcb-0867-4767-bcde-722a11cb2fa3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d9094669-8f83-4345-972f-9224c672d65e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기준</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a0c845b-2cb3-4b88-a841-85607b6ae71a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6261d38b-e207-49c8-8516-6df3d4726a6f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">전개도가 A4 안에 들어가는 사이즈</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72544f5f-f276-4dac-9a45-95ae399b2a9c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f23a893-99d6-440a-a3de-74227d3a3d6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71b6ccf1-eda2-4c2a-9df9-7d7668ae5724\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-034b2508-90f4-477a-879a-b24fa4922338\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7627a263-7153-4deb-a2c8-a486397f8b10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0083f73a-8c1f-40ff-8712-b534534ab443\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디지털 &lt;= 오프셋</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd16da34-ca90-4582-9eda-fe8b5a4c1ac9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-098e75f0-76e5-4ad5-9f90-b30e5884ec26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오프셋이 조금이라도 더 비쌉니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2184459-6db4-41e4-96b6-6ce086622610\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83ad1cbc-dc52-4ec8-94a4-0d8e3446493f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cdf8b9f-f9b2-496b-828b-ad06d4f44806\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cfdfa122-490b-4764-9bb5-bc16a3740771\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79ac62f1-66d8-4cd7-babe-e13927a7d557\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d5e72fa-e660-49c0-a78d-412712d548ec\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디지털 &lt;= 오프셋</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c44d2667-77e6-4bed-9490-db6a02083e4e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-643af971-2e9d-46c4-ab35-99dc2f10ae4b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오프셋 2~4일 더 걸립니다. 디지털은 단 2~3일에 납품될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a7c0a7b-056b-4fcd-b251-c03caceadb85\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-627f2a0f-d813-4fff-8057-91aacef3a38c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e2d0f25f-d949-48e0-bace-a1ddcd20bc2f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-80c9a9d3-7e93-4685-8ea1-3f0725bc2d7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>퀄리티</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20eb10b0-fd90-41b0-b6a7-bebf21bba942\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5492392-2a19-49a6-acea-c62741ac6de4\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디지털 &lt;= 오프셋</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3be60c36-5649-4e1b-afdc-b5c8cd450fd0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ce4186b-7b6a-4439-90be-bda064907748\" style=\"color:#555555;\">퀄리티는 아직은 오프셋 방식이 워너입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf6e4480-7abb-46e5-98cf-d204a49783b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3316b67-a185-4da6-84dd-ea3f460bc3ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-39a2fbd3-18bf-4e46-a10d-bd33e01a5603\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-738123af-83f8-4f0e-806d-7b4dfa22ff60\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-208dce2d-1461-492d-ae5d-a8b4005be44d\" style=\"\">디지털 방식의 장점</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2bc8622e-c5f1-4a2e-a373-de824663d6e4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e078b51-c102-4321-8c5b-ea606ede389d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9add0010-a14e-4368-b432-99cc29289e39\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털의 장점은 아무래도 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d6284813-31fa-4f01-9b8c-e39fe95f514c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>소량이 가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5a2df075-a773-41ff-9d22-643d53603980\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하다는 것입니다. 오프셋은 소량이 거의 불가능합니다. 10개를 오프셋으로 하면 500개를 하는 단가나 방식이 거의 유사하므로 고객님께서 손해를 보시게 되어 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8bc47e41-3d51-4467-80cb-25fa17322af4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-808a78af-4ab6-4c63-82e7-cbf5698755f7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e67f22e1-1581-44db-be05-65770a100a14\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1dbb685c-ce7c-4379-92f8-57c5f7200498\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bf728a7c-98bd-4755-bff7-5ef2208bb90d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기가 빠릅니다</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f581aa1-9dbd-4582-a47f-4642cb150d60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">. 오프셋은 준비 기간이나 목형 제작시간 등이 소요됩니다. 또한 종이 발주나 인쇄 출력도 시간이 소요될 수 있습니다. 하지만 디지털 인쇄는 이런 과정이 거의 생략되어 납기를 단축시킬 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48d49296-7a45-4b1f-a6a7-9d87a956f4c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e44623e-d028-45ff-b884-9967f2ebf3f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8667b8ad-6076-472a-b149-89d9c7860cfb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-454cf8cb-4445-4502-8ce4-a39a1c44023b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 디지털의 단점은 퀄리티입니다. 특히 인쇄보다는 커팅의 퀄리티가 아무래도 도무송보다는 좋지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-710c431a-cedf-41b2-9695-1e2a05c71069\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:675px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223874188357/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b615177-5211-4854-8db8-97996d109d77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:841px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223874188357/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d195b382-2f8a-460d-b128-ffe53845ab4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c113b0de-aab3-402c-b95b-5396ae65bd93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c00ec39-2deb-44d9-b887-d800b20882f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이해를 돕기 위해 과장해서 클로즈업 사진을 드려봅니다. 코팅을 하고 커팅압을 조절하면 완전히 저급의 퀄리티로 나오지는 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd51dddb-1f40-4ecb-b9ca-4aeb9f062f07\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50e52ab1-0c3d-4654-9df6-542a3c10ceb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-665d84bc-fc29-4245-840f-92d9d64b9a08\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09601893-1b21-4793-93ae-be0c4a46eb6f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음에는 더 자세히 오프셋 방식에 대해 작성해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a76032cb-7428-4d28-9ebf-61cd3d4035ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f40e454-8baa-4b2e-9d71-e2064d246057\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d6405238-0be8-4575-9676-4cbe405797c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f051ffa-2b03-4690-b861-b17c681e0253\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6404fc1-3f7a-47ae-ba38-5df0b49a6fce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d38b4d6-0fb9-49da-afd4-dfc2198a4436\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 아무리 디지털 소량이라도 최고의 퀄리티로 생산하기 위해 최선의 노력을 다하고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fd3407a-1a61-4128-9bf0-c8927ddef61c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c682c215-ceb6-4e0e-8bd5-5e847aa4fc2c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03f51c8e-8528-4979-8715-052e622b2e8e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ec1538aa-951c-4ef9-b943-76576335bbb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지 솔루션이 궁금하신 인쇄업체는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c7fab20a-3be7-4591-a9ab-9d4e19599800\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd89ac23-629d-4eb7-be2a-df8b67f28d40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음 블로그 글을 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-31cb9db4-4b2a-45a2-8c92-541048ff2df0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0905c568-261c-49c7-8033-d4483bfe272c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-93ca3e1e-d347-40b0-a3dc-8a5e35dbb025\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" 